OL,3,CUse of heritage names for ITV regional
OL,4,Cnews programmes
OL,6,GIs it time for ITV to rebrand some of
OL,7,Gits English regional news services?
OL,9,FThe names of some of the regional news
OL,10,Fprogrammes echo the old company names
OL,11,Frather than the regions they serve.
OL,13,FAnd in some cases the link is not
OL,14,Fobvious.
OL,16,FTake ITV News Meridian ` the service
OL,17,Fcovering much of the south and south
OL,18,Feast of England.
