OL,6,FSince the last round of changes to
OL,7,FITV's regional provision in 2013,
OL,8,FMeridian has provided 30 minutes of
OL,9,Fdistinct news for the south and south
OL,10,Feast each day at 6pm plus a sub opt
OL,11,Ffor the former Thames Valley region.
OL,13,FThe name Meridian means "of the
OL,14,Fsouth". It was, of course, the name of
OL,15,Fthe company which won the franchise
OL,16,Ffrom TVS and took over from 1993.
