OL,6,FBut Meridian's brand only lasted for
OL,7,Fsix years before it started to be
OL,8,Fdisplaced by the ITV brand name. Like
OL,9,Fother English regional station names
OL,10,Fit was consigned to a secondary role
OL,11,Fin 2002 before disappearing completely
OL,12,Fas a station name when regular
OL,13,Fregional output other than news came
OL,14,Fto an end a few years later.
OL,16,FI'd bet a large number of people who
OL,17,Flive in the south and south east do
OL,18,Fnot realise they are in the Meridian
OL,19,Fregion. A corporate name for a region
OL,20,Fwhich stretches from Dorset to the
OL,21,FThames Estuary and includes territory
OL,22,Fwhich once belonged to Central.
