OL,6,FA simple name like ITV News South at
OL,7,Fleast avoids pretentious affectation.
OL,9,FAlternatively why not brand the two
OL,10,Feditions separately? ITV News South
OL,11,Fand ITV News South East would
OL,12,Fhighlight the fact two distinct
OL,13,Feditions of the programme are produced.
OL,15,FThere are other anomalies.
OL,17,FDoes the name ITV News Anglia make
OL,18,Fsense to viewers in Luton or the
OL,19,Ffringes of the Midlands?
