OL,6,FDoes ITV News Calendar only work
OL,7,Fbecause of the historic strength of
OL,8,FCalendar? It also avoids the use of
OL,9,Fthe word Yorkshire in a service also
OL,10,Fcovering Lincolnshire and the North
OL,11,FMidlands?
OL,13,FIn the Border region, the bulletins
OL,14,Fare branded as ITV News Border but the
OL,15,Fmain programme is ITV News Lookaround
OL,16,F` all presented from Tyne Tees in
OL,17,FGateshead.
OL,19,FAnd don't get me started on the
OL,20,Fcontinuing use of the name Granada
OL,21,FReports ` 20 years after Granada
OL,22,Fdisappeared as a company.
