OL,6,FIf all those names were only the names
OL,7,Fof the TV news services it would be
OL,8,Fjust about possible to argue for their
OL,9,Fretention ` they refer to the
OL,10,Fprogrammes or regions subsumed into
OL,11,FITV plc and respect the local heritage.
OL,13,FBut they are also the names of the
OL,14,Fregional services on itv.com/news.
OL,15,FThose who are too young to remember
OL,16,FITV as a federal system ` who should
OL,17,Fbe one of the website's target
OL,18,Faudiences ` must be mightily confused.
